           * With IMAGE, if an image is 100 x 200 pixels, mapping the image onto the entire
           * size of a quad would require the points (0,0) (100, 0) (100,200) (0,200).
           * The same mapping in NORMAL is (0,0) (1,0) (1,1) (0,1).
